{"tid":1727218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黎明行動] Shall we Strike 主題曲","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:35.000Z","uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4943709c23afdb6eba75e397689b7e485b1ed331","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">徵求：音樂人演唱。</span></strong><br />\n然後我哋在塞鐵時聚人，播歌一齊唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n（原曲： 陳奕迅 Shall we talk<br />\n原曲link：<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7MO58UGhZdk）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7MO58UGhZdk%EF%BC%89&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQKHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=3f55bd4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7MO58UGhZdk）</a><br />\n<br />\n改版歌詞第一版（歡迎俾意見！）：<br />\n<br />\n明月光　為何又照地堂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明月光    孩童在那路旁</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n寧願在公園躲藏　不想喝湯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">凌晨在子彈邊緣    天真去擋</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任由目光　留在漫畫一角<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">若然目光    停留在公司看</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為何望母親一眼就如罰留堂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為何望有天公義自由天空降</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n孩童只盼望歡樂　大人只知道期望<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">孩童想捍衛希望    大人只知道量度<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n為何都不太懂得努力體恤對方<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從來不知道身處現場多麼怯慌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大門外有蟋蟀　迴響卻如同幻覺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽迷霧裡高歌    迴響似黎明號角：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nShall we talk　Shall we talk<br />\n就當重新手拖手去上學堂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;Shall we strike, shall we strike<br />\n願意罷工今天休假拒絕忙&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陪我講　陪我講出我們最後何以生疏<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>陪你塞    陪你塞到鐵路尾站完再Encore</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n誰怕講　誰會可悲得過孤獨探戈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">誰怕塞    誰要天天工作失去太多<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n難得　可以同座　何以　要忌諱赤裸<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列車    不過延誤    何以    要動怒發火</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果心聲真有療效　誰怕暴露更多　你別怕我<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果返工真有療效    誰要動亂更多    你別怪我</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n螢幕發光　無論什麼都看<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前路有光    還留在公司看</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n情人在分手邊緣    只敢喝湯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">孩童在子彈邊緣    開遮去擋</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若沉默似金　還談什麼戀愛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">若人命要緊    還談什麼工作</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n寧願在發聲機器面前笑著忙   <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沉默在國家機器面前似賣傻</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成人只寄望收穫　情人只聽見承諾<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人人都看重收穫　但良知聽見求助</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為何都不太懂得努力珍惜對方<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從前不知道身處現場多麼怯慌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n螳螂面對蟋蟀　迴響也如同幻覺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在迷霧裡高歌    迴響似黎明號角：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nShall we talk　Shall we talk<br />\n就算牙關開始打震　別說謊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Shall we strike, shall we fight <br />\n就算明天多麼可怕    別再拖<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n陪我講　陪我講出我們最後何以生疏<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陪你塞    陪你塞到鐵路尾站完再Encore</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n誰怕講　誰會可悲得過孤獨探戈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">誰怕塞    誰要天天工作失去太多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n難得　可以同座　何以　要忌諱赤裸<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列車    不過延誤    何以    要動怒發火</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果心聲真有療效　誰怕暴露更多<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果返工真有療效    誰要動亂更多    </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n陪我講　陪我親身正視眼淚誰跌得多<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陪我塞    陪我堅守信念眼淚誰去撫摸 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無法講　   除非彼此已失去了能力觸摸<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無法躲       明天香港已經變了無望之邦<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n鈴聲　可以寧靜　難過　卻避不過<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列車    可以延誤    人性    卻別冷藏<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n如果沉默太沉重　別要輕輕帶過<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果時代太沉重　亦要今天反抗<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n明月光　為何未照地堂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明月光    為何又再推搪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n孩兒在公司很忙　不需喝湯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">孩童在天台邊緣    只等你幫<br />\n</span></strong><br />\nAnd shall we talk　斜陽白趕一趟<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">And shall we strike  為時代闖一趟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n沉默令我聽得見葉兒聲聲降<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明在遠方光復自由天空朗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何建議/ 推薦，歡迎pm Telegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/Karas8964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKaras8964&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQKHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=055a3ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Karas8964</a>"},{"pid":"5210cabe1f647b3bb160f1863628402961542074","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99d91b8488b590d4127c02eabb90c8ac48644b52","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be2fbcda568de8de94550a15a95655369edef190","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f83fd24493ca4c83be1d140429124db8b72e73c","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a530d738269c87ff0acfb02d7bf46a68ee5edaa","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f77d0e8e4ed16958efb1b30fa5caf739248c474","tid":1727218,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}